originalText.text: Vivian is my go-to real estate agent! I've known her since she started and it's been amazing to see her grow both as a friend and a client. Her professional, consistent, and genuine approach to her work really inspires me to be better at what I do as well. I just wish I knew more buyers and sellers to introduce to her!

originalText.text:
Vivian Kuo is a highly skilled and professional real estate agent. She possesses a unique combination of qualities that make her stand out in the industry, accomplishing goals with speed and efficiency thanks to her dedication.
Her knowledge of the NYC market is impressive and her connections in the industry are vast.  She provided valuable advice and recommendations throughout the preparation process which made it a stress free experience.

Vivian has a natural ability to inspire confidence and her positive attitude helped keep us calm and engaged during the selling process. She was able to navigate any obstacles that came up and was able to close the deal in record time.

If you are looking to buy or sell property in NYC, I highly recommend Vivian Kuo.  A true professional, one of the best in the business.

originalText.text: Vivian is one of the most professional, hard-working, capable agents I know. I often refer her because I trust clients will be in good hands. What I like about Vivian is that she's attentive and patient. She'll go the extra mile and walk you to the finish line. She never breaks the flow of communication. Most importantly, she works as your agent and not a project. Our family is grateful for her hard work.

originalText.text: Vivian represented us as we sold our co-op recently. I was both impressed and encouraged by how hard she worked to sell our home as the market turned against us. She was a strong advocate and gave good advice along the way. Importantly, she also really listened to our thoughts and desires during the process. Not only did we get a number of great offers, the process to close was very smooth. A great person to partner with you if you are selling or buying.
